PrecisAmendment to the PLEASURE CRAFT SEWAGE POLLUTION PREVENTION REGULATIONS which will prohibit the operator of a pleasure boat from depositing sewage into the following waters in Manitoba: the Red River (from the U.S. border to Lake Winnipeg), the Assiniboine River (from the Red River upstream to St. James Bridge in Winnipeg), and Shoal Lake.

precis:
Amendment to the PLEASURE CRAFT SEWAGE POLLUTION PREVENTION REGULATIONS
which will prohibit the operator of a pleasure boat from depositing sewage
into the following waters in Manitoba:  the Red River (from the U.S. border
to Lake Winnipeg), the Assiniboine River (from the Red River upstream to
St. James Bridge in Winnipeg), and Shoal Lake.
